{"tid":675874,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[我有自殺傾向...]有冇人睇過精神科/心理輔導???","createTime":"2018-05-24T02:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T08:33:36.000Z","uid":33058,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"41f1457ed7b930bd3dbc8774d3084d2517c49907","tid":675874,"uid":33058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:01:20.000Z","msg":"我有自殺傾向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得社工/精神科/心理輔導冇乜用<br />\n中學果陣睇過, 而家問題仍然存在<br />\n都6, 7年前既事<br />\n如果成日都要見精神科又解決唔到既, <br />\n我寧願死<br />\n<br />\n我唔想搞到人, 我想慢性咁死<br />\n因為我每日咁樣生活都好大壓力<br />\n生不如死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我怕死唔去比人笑我殘廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n(試過跳樓比人用力扯番走...)<br />\n想諗方法慢慢咁粹死, <br />\n因為我知我唔應該留係呢個世界上<br />\n<br />\n如果巴打們可以既, 笑我垃圾, 我就好快會好多怨恨, <br />\n做d自己控制唔到既事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最後, 如果真係有精神科 / 心理輔導既可唔可以講下點樣幫到自己/睇過既經歷</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/waste_ching\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwaste_ching&d=h5CBWGnPckCkRoAY9OKbogHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=21d09909\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/waste_ching</a><br />\n冇account既可以tg"},{"pid":"444397dd3e3737880d779d268c954d4b4b149e7c","tid":675874,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"醫生話你咩事？"},{"pid":"1ec3c654a939de2286e5a79800e3145585838d61","tid":675874,"uid":33058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444397dd3e3737880d779d268c954d4b4b149e7c","tid":675874,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"醫生話你咩事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"我都唔知, 好似幫唔到我咁, 剩係叫我食藥<br />\n6, 7年前考HKALE去過明心樓睇<br 